<main id="main" class="enterprise-page" data-enterprise-vision>
  <section class="enterprise-hero"><div class="shell"><p class="os-eyebrow">BUSINESS OF MEDICINE INTELLIGENCE</p><h1>The intelligence platforms behind better physician decisions.</h1><p>Every Decision Episode contributes anonymously to one Business of Medicine intelligence platform. These platforms are currently being built. They will never expose individual physicians.</p><p class="enterprise-status">STATUS: IN DEVELOPMENT · Physician value first · Individual physician data is never sold.</p></div></section>
  <section class="enterprise-architecture"><div class="shell"><p class="os-eyebrow">THE CONTENT ENGINE</p><h2>Every Decision Episode has exactly one home.</h2><ol><li>Decision Episode</li><li>One Intelligence Platform</li><li>Anonymous aggregation</li><li>Validation</li><li>Physician guidance improves</li><li>Enterprise deliverable</li></ol><p>The mapping is mandatory and 1:1: Compensation maps to Compensation Intelligence™; Employment Contracts maps to Contract Intelligence™; AI in Practice maps to AI Adoption Intelligence™. Nothing enters the library without a single named Intelligence Platform.</p></div></section>
  <section class="enterprise-principles"><div class="shell"><p class="os-eyebrow">WHAT IS BEING BUILT</p><h2>One physician-first content engine. Nine future intelligence platforms.</h2><div class="enterprise-process"><article><b>01 · PHYSICIAN VALUE</b><h3>Start with a useful decision.</h3><p>Each Episode is uniquely written for physicians and deliberately serves recognition in 30 seconds, understanding in 2 minutes, and execution in 5 minutes.</p></article><article><b>02 · ANONYMOUS AGGREGATION</b><h3>Patterns only in groups.</h3><p>Decision patterns can improve guidance and future intelligence only after minimum aggregation requirements are met.</p></article><article><b>03 · VALIDATED DELIVERY</b><h3>Evidence before inference.</h3><p>Every future deliverable has an explicit buyer, validation requirement, privacy safeguard, and limitation.</p></article></div></div></section>
  <section class="enterprise-products"><div class="shell"><p class="os-eyebrow">INTELLIGENCE PLATFORMS</p><h2>What each platform becomes.</h2><p class="enterprise-intro">Open a platform to see its physician benefit, enterprise use, required evidence, aggregation threshold, and privacy protections.</p><div class="enterprise-product-grid" data-enterprise-products><details id="compensation"><summary><span>STATUS: IN DEVELOPMENT</span><h3>Compensation Intelligence™</h3><p>Anonymous physician compensation models, negotiation outcomes, productivity structures, and compensation trends.</p><b>Learn more <i aria-hidden="true">→</i></b></summary><div><p><b>Primary Business of Medicine domain:</b> Compensation</p><p><b>Primary enterprise buyer:</b> Large health systems</p><p><b>Primary enterprise deliverable:</b> Aggregate compensation design and negotiation-pattern brief.</p><p><b>Primary physician value:</b> A clearer formula, terms to question, and better preparation for compensation conversations.</p><p><b>Decision Episodes feeding the platform:</b> Compensation only. Every Decision Episode maps 1:1 to exactly one Intelligence Platform.</p><p><b>Minimum aggregation requirements:</b> Minimum 30 validated anonymous outcome records across at least 5 organizations; no reportable cell below 10.</p><p><b>Minimum validation requirements:</b> Structured episode completion, source taxonomy review, and outcome consistency checks.</p><p><b>Privacy safeguards:</b> No names, employers, offers, raw contracts, or individual benchmarks.</p><p><b>Development status:</b> Episode foundation active; intelligence product in development.</p></div></details><details id="contracts"><summary><span>STATUS: IN DEVELOPMENT</span><h3>Contract Intelligence™</h3><p>Employment structures, restrictive covenants, offer terms, and negotiation patterns.</p><b>Learn more <i aria-hidden="true">→</i></b></summary><div><p><b>Primary Business of Medicine domain:</b> Employment Contracts</p><p><b>Primary enterprise buyer:</b> Recruiters</p><p><b>Primary enterprise deliverable:</b> Aggregate contract-term and negotiation-pattern brief.</p><p><b>Primary physician value:</b> A practical, physician-first review of terms, leverage, and restrictions.</p><p><b>Decision Episodes feeding the platform:</b> Employment Contracts only. Every Decision Episode maps 1:1 to exactly one Intelligence Platform.</p><p><b>Minimum aggregation requirements:</b> Minimum 30 validated anonymous outcome records across at least 5 organizations; no reportable cell below 10.</p><p><b>Minimum validation requirements:</b> Clause-topic taxonomy review, structured completion, and outcome consistency checks.</p><p><b>Privacy safeguards:</b> No contracts, employer names, negotiation histories, or individual profiles.</p><p><b>Development status:</b> Decision Episode and intelligence product in development.</p></div></details><details id="ai-adoption"><summary><span>STATUS: IN DEVELOPMENT</span><h3>AI Adoption Intelligence™</h3><p>Clinical AI, operational AI, ambient documentation, practice workflow, measured adoption, and real-world value.</p><b>Learn more <i aria-hidden="true">→</i></b></summary><div><p><b>Primary Business of Medicine domain:</b> Artificial Intelligence in Practice</p><p><b>Primary enterprise buyer:</b> AI companies</p><p><b>Primary enterprise deliverable:</b> Aggregate adoption-readiness and workflow-value brief.</p><p><b>Primary physician value:</b> A measured way to choose, pilot, oversee, and assess AI in practice.</p><p><b>Decision Episodes feeding the platform:</b> Artificial Intelligence in Practice only. Every Decision Episode maps 1:1 to exactly one Intelligence Platform.</p><p><b>Minimum aggregation requirements:</b> Minimum 30 validated anonymous outcome records across at least 5 organizations; no reportable cell below 10.</p><p><b>Minimum validation requirements:</b> Workflow-use taxonomy review, structured pilot reflections, and value-measure consistency checks.</p><p><b>Privacy safeguards:</b> No patient data, tool-user profiles, or identifiable performance data.</p><p><b>Development status:</b> Decision Episode and intelligence product in development.</p></div></details><details id="revenue-cycle"><summary><span>STATUS: IN DEVELOPMENT</span><h3>Revenue Cycle Intelligence™</h3><p>Coding, billing, denials, documentation, and revenue optimization.</p><b>Learn more <i aria-hidden="true">→</i></b></summary><div><p><b>Primary Business of Medicine domain:</b> Revenue Cycle</p><p><b>Primary enterprise buyer:</b> Revenue cycle companies</p><p><b>Primary enterprise deliverable:</b> Aggregate revenue-cycle decision-friction report.</p><p><b>Primary physician value:</b> A clearer route through documentation, coding, billing, and escalation choices.</p><p><b>Decision Episodes feeding the platform:</b> Revenue Cycle only. Every Decision Episode maps 1:1 to exactly one Intelligence Platform.</p><p><b>Minimum aggregation requirements:</b> Minimum 30 validated anonymous outcome records across at least 5 organizations; no reportable cell below 10.</p><p><b>Minimum validation requirements:</b> Validated topic taxonomy, structured outcomes, and setting consistency checks.</p><p><b>Privacy safeguards:</b> No patient data, claims, billing records, or individual performance reporting.</p><p><b>Development status:</b> Domain and Decision Episode in development.</p></div></details><details id="practice-economics"><summary><span>STATUS: IN DEVELOPMENT</span><h3>Practice Economics Intelligence™</h3><p>Staffing, operations, practice performance, equipment, ancillary services, and efficiency.</p><b>Learn more <i aria-hidden="true">→</i></b></summary><div><p><b>Primary Business of Medicine domain:</b> Practice Economics</p><p><b>Primary enterprise buyer:</b> Practice management organizations</p><p><b>Primary enterprise deliverable:</b> Aggregate practice-economics signal brief.</p><p><b>Primary physician value:</b> A physician-readable framework for operating and economic tradeoffs.</p><p><b>Decision Episodes feeding the platform:</b> Practice Economics only. Every Decision Episode maps 1:1 to exactly one Intelligence Platform.</p><p><b>Minimum aggregation requirements:</b> Minimum 30 validated anonymous outcome records across at least 5 organizations; no reportable cell below 10.</p><p><b>Minimum validation requirements:</b> Decision taxonomy review, structured scenario outcomes, and setting consistency checks.</p><p><b>Privacy safeguards:</b> No financial statements, named practices, or individual earnings data.</p><p><b>Development status:</b> Domain and Decision Episode in development.</p></div></details><details id="practice-ownership"><summary><span>STATUS: IN DEVELOPMENT</span><h3>Practice Ownership Intelligence™</h3><p>Employment, partnership, ownership, private equity, succession, and transitions.</p><b>Learn more <i aria-hidden="true">→</i></b></summary><div><p><b>Primary Business of Medicine domain:</b> Practice Ownership</p><p><b>Primary enterprise buyer:</b> Banks</p><p><b>Primary enterprise deliverable:</b> Aggregate ownership-pathway and transition brief.</p><p><b>Primary physician value:</b> A clearer way to evaluate control, risk, ownership paths, and transitions.</p><p><b>Decision Episodes feeding the platform:</b> Practice Ownership only. Every Decision Episode maps 1:1 to exactly one Intelligence Platform.</p><p><b>Minimum aggregation requirements:</b> Minimum 30 validated anonymous outcome records across at least 5 organizations; no reportable cell below 10.</p><p><b>Minimum validation requirements:</b> Ownership-pathway taxonomy review, structured outcomes, and model consistency checks.</p><p><b>Privacy safeguards:</b> No transaction documents, valuations, named buyers, or identifiable profiles.</p><p><b>Development status:</b> Decision Episode and intelligence product in development.</p></div></details><details id="leadership-operations"><summary><span>STATUS: IN DEVELOPMENT</span><h3>Leadership &amp; Operations Intelligence™</h3><p>Leadership decisions, governance, medical director roles, department operations, and management.</p><b>Learn more <i aria-hidden="true">→</i></b></summary><div><p><b>Primary Business of Medicine domain:</b> Leadership &amp; Operations</p><p><b>Primary enterprise buyer:</b> Health systems</p><p><b>Primary enterprise deliverable:</b> Aggregate leadership and operations decision brief.</p><p><b>Primary physician value:</b> Practical support for governance, leadership, and operational decisions.</p><p><b>Decision Episodes feeding the platform:</b> Leadership &amp; Operations only. Every Decision Episode maps 1:1 to exactly one Intelligence Platform.</p><p><b>Minimum aggregation requirements:</b> Minimum 30 validated anonymous outcome records across at least 5 organizations; no reportable cell below 10.</p><p><b>Minimum validation requirements:</b> Decision-context taxonomy review, structured outcomes, and role/setting consistency checks.</p><p><b>Privacy safeguards:</b> No employee-performance profiles or identifiable team reporting.</p><p><b>Development status:</b> Decision Episode and intelligence product in development.</p></div></details><details id="physician-wealth"><summary><span>STATUS: IN DEVELOPMENT</span><h3>Physician Wealth Intelligence™</h3><p>Retirement, asset allocation, tax planning, insurance, and financial decision patterns.</p><b>Learn more <i aria-hidden="true">→</i></b></summary><div><p><b>Primary Business of Medicine domain:</b> Physician Wealth</p><p><b>Primary enterprise buyer:</b> Financial institutions</p><p><b>Primary enterprise deliverable:</b> Aggregate physician financial-decision needs brief.</p><p><b>Primary physician value:</b> A clearer foundation for financial choices across a physician career.</p><p><b>Decision Episodes feeding the platform:</b> Physician Wealth only. Every Decision Episode maps 1:1 to exactly one Intelligence Platform.</p><p><b>Minimum aggregation requirements:</b> Minimum 30 validated anonymous outcome records across at least 5 organizations; no reportable cell below 10.</p><p><b>Minimum validation requirements:</b> Financial-decision taxonomy review, structured outcomes, and career-stage consistency checks.</p><p><b>Privacy safeguards:</b> No account data, balances, portfolios, insurance applications, or individual financial profiles.</p><p><b>Development status:</b> Decision Episode and intelligence product in development.</p></div></details><details id="technology-adoption"><summary><span>STATUS: IN DEVELOPMENT</span><h3>Technology Adoption Intelligence™</h3><p>Practice technology, patient communication, workflow tools, and operational software.</p><b>Learn more <i aria-hidden="true">→</i></b></summary><div><p><b>Primary Business of Medicine domain:</b> Technology Adoption</p><p><b>Primary enterprise buyer:</b> Technology vendors</p><p><b>Primary enterprise deliverable:</b> Aggregate implementation-readiness brief.</p><p><b>Primary physician value:</b> A practical way to select, implement, and assess technology in practice.</p><p><b>Decision Episodes feeding the platform:</b> Technology Adoption only. Every Decision Episode maps 1:1 to exactly one Intelligence Platform.</p><p><b>Minimum aggregation requirements:</b> Minimum 30 validated anonymous outcome records across at least 5 organizations; no reportable cell below 10.</p><p><b>Minimum validation requirements:</b> Technology-decision taxonomy review, structured implementation outcomes, and setting consistency checks.</p><p><b>Privacy safeguards:</b> No vendor-user tracking, patient data, or identifiable adoption profiles.</p><p><b>Development status:</b> Domain and Decision Episode in development.</p></div></details></div></div></section>
  <section class="enterprise-governance"><div class="shell enterprise-governance-grid"><div><p class="os-eyebrow">GOVERNANCE</p><h2>Trust is a product requirement.</h2><p>No intelligence product is available until its aggregation and validation conditions are met. Physician Decision Episodes remain free.</p></div><ul><li>Aggregated intelligence only</li><li>No individual physician data sales</li><li>No patient data or raw documents</li><li>Transparent methodology and limitations</li><li>Minimum valid samples before any output</li><li>One Episode maps to one platform</li></ul></div></section>
  <section class="enterprise-methodology"><div class="shell"><p class="os-eyebrow">CONTENT STANDARD</p><h2>Useful enough to change the next decision.</h2><p>Decision Episodes are original physician-specific work: distilled from credible public thinking, organized for a real decision, illustrated with practical tools, and never copied or generic.</p><a class="os-text-link" href="{{@site.url}}/methodology/">Explore the methodology <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></div></section>
